# CORE: agnostic
# Project v2 board number for this repo's owner — the <n> in the board
# URL: github.com/users/<owner>/projects/<n> (or /orgs/<owner>/...).
#
# Preferred source of truth for server-side board sync
# (project-status-labeled.yml) and the session skills. Committed so every
# surface — desktop and web/mobile sessions, and the workflows — can read
# it without `gh variable get`.
#
# Leave the value empty for labels-only mode (no board): the sync
# workflow logs a notice and does nothing.
#
# Back-compat: if this is empty/absent, board sync falls back to the legacy
# PROJECT_NUMBER repo variable (pre-v1.11 installs). When both are set they
# must name the SAME project — verify.sh validates they agree.
PROJECT_NUMBER=3
